dct_description_sm: Map of Boćki and the surrounding region during a time when Poland was a Russian province. Relief shown by contours, shading and spot heights. In upper margin: Karte des westlichen Russlands. M31. Boćki. Includes guide to adjoining maps.
dct_publisher_sm: [Berlin] : Kartographische Abteilung d. Königl. Preuss. Landes-Aufnahme, 1915.
